data.description: Spacious 2 story home on 3.10 acres. Enjoy the beautiful high on the hill views, away from the city. Big house with tons of space to spread out in. Two laundry room locations, one the main and second floor. Kitchen needs a face lift. Home is all electric. Currently listed below assessed value!!
